OL,3,COver 200 UK firms now have a four-day
OL,4,Cworkweek with full pay
OL,6,FMore than 200 UK companies have
OL,7,Fswitched to a permanent four-day
OL,8,Fworking week with no pay loss,
OL,9,Faccording to research by a campaign
OL,10,Fgroup.
OL,12,FThis marks the latest milestone in the
OL,13,Fcampaign to reinvent the way British
OL,14,Fpeople work, the 4 Day Week Foundation
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FThe companies range from marketing
OL,18,Fagencies, IT firms and consultancies
OL,19,Fto non-profit organisations employing
OL,20,Fmore than 5,000 people.
