OL,3,COver 200 UK firms now have a four-day
OL,4,Cworkweek with full pay
OL,6,FThe foundation's campaign director Joe
OL,7,FRyle said the five-day week was
OL,8,F"invented 100 years ago" and is "no
OL,9,Flonger fit for purpose".
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FHe said: "With 50% more free time, a
OL,17,Ffour-day week gives people the freedom
OL,18,Fto live happier, more fulfilling
OL,19,Flives."
