OL,3,COver 200 UK firms now have a four-day
OL,4,Cworkweek with full pay
OL,6,FSupporters of the policy say that
OL,7,Fcommitting to shorter weeks is a
OL,8,Fuseful way to attract and retain
OL,9,Femployees but also improve their
OL,10,Foverall wellbeing.
OL,12,FSo far London-based companies are the
OL,13,Fmost enthusiastic, making up 59 of the
OL,14,F200 companies that adopted the policy.
OL,16,FWhile four-day weeks are growing in
OL,17,Fpopularity, many employees are still
OL,18,Fbattling to continue to work from
OL,19,Fhome, let alone have a shorter week.
