OL,3,COver 200 UK firms now have a four-day
OL,4,Cworkweek with full pay
OL,6,FIn the US, investment bank JP Morgan
OL,7,Fand tech giant Amazon have demanded
OL,8,Fthat staff return to the office full
OL,9,Ftime, despite having allowed hybrid
OL,10,Fworking patterns since the Covid-19
OL,11,Fpandemic.
OL,13,FA new survey by Spark Market Research
OL,14,Fhas revealed that 78% of 18- to 34-
OL,15,Fyear-olds believe a four-day working
OL,16,Fweek will become the norm within the
OL,17,Fnext five years, while 65% said they
OL,18,Fare opposed to a return to traditional
OL,19,Ffull-time office working.
