OL,3,COver 200 UK firms now have a four-day
OL,4,Cworkweek with full pay
OL,6,FLynsey Carolan, managing director of
OL,7,FSpark, said that this age group, which
OL,8,Fwill form the core of the workforce
OL,9,Ffor the next 50 years, is clearly
OL,10,Fsignalling its intention to not return
OL,11,Fto old fashioned working patterns.
OL,13,FShe also highlighted that mental
OL,14,Fhealth and improving overall wellbeing
OL,15,F"are top priorities" for this
OL,16,Fgeneration, making the four-day week a
OL,17,Fmeaningful benefit and key
OL,18,Fcontributing factor to their quality
OL,19,Fof life.
